577
00:24:28,830 --> 00:24:29,430
To go to Feng Yu.

578
00:24:30,110 --> 00:24:30,800
How about I go with you?

579
00:24:31,440 --> 00:24:32,270
Forget it.

580
00:24:32,520 --> 00:24:34,040
