592
00:25:45,910 --> 00:25:47,160
How have you been?

593
00:25:47,430 --> 00:25:48,550
Are you feeling better?

594
00:25:49,470 --> 00:25:51,540
Have you received the fabric I gave you last time?

595
00:25:52,950 --> 00:25:54,230
Yes. Thank you.

596
00:25:54,910 --> 00:25:57,190
Feng always tells me that you have good taste,

597
00:25:57,210 --> 00:25:57,850
