598
00:25:58,000 --> 00:25:59,800
Only good fabric is suitable for you.

599
00:26:00,450 --> 00:26:01,470
I have good taste?

600
00:26:02,070 --> 00:26:03,380
If I had good taste,

601
00:26:03,590 --> 00:26:05,030
I wouldn't marry him.

602
00:26:05,550 --> 00:26:06,550
I was out of mind.

603
00:26:08,630 --> 00:26:09,070
Ms.

604
00:26:10,030 --> 00:26:11,670
I know a very good tailor.

605
00:26:12,100 --> 00:26:14,270
He's a very famous cheongsam-maker.

606
00:26:14,730 --> 00:26:15,770
Are you free today?

607
00:26:16,510 --> 00:26:17,950
My car's outside. I can drive you there.

608
00:26:18,590 --> 00:26:20,270
You want to send me away

609
00:26:20,440 --> 00:26:21,640
so that Feng

610
00:26:21,670 --> 00:26:23,230
can be with his Bao, right?

611
00:26:24,250 --> 00:26:24,690
Go away.

612
00:26:26,400 --> 00:26:27,080
Ms.

613
00:26:27,830 --> 00:26:28,950
There's no Bao at all.

614
00:26:28,970 --> 00:26:30,150
That's just a joke.

615
00:26:30,180 --> 00:26:31,020
Don't take it seriously.

616
00:26:31,390 --> 00:26:33,680
I came to see him for business.

617
00:26:33,830 --> 00:26:34,710
What business?

618
00:26:35,270 --> 00:26:37,060
We are discussing to go north.

619
00:26:37,950 --> 00:26:38,560
Ms.

620
00:26:39,080 --> 00:26:40,240
The price of scrap steel there

621
00:26:40,270 --> 00:26:41,670
