622
00:26:41,960 --> 00:26:43,000
If the market is satisfying,

623
00:26:43,030 --> 00:26:44,190
we can sell it at twice the price.

624
00:26:44,550 --> 00:26:45,710
I just want

625
00:26:45,740 --> 00:26:47,270
