644
00:27:35,510 --> 00:27:37,070
She can treat me however she likes.

645
00:27:37,420 --> 00:27:38,690
I'm certainly much more tolerant than her.

646
00:27:39,070 --> 00:27:40,400
You scared me to death.

647
00:27:41,650 --> 00:27:42,890
