00:31:02,290 --> 00:31:03,810
I really don't have enough money.

750
00:31:05,270 --> 00:31:06,540
I still have to build that storage yard.

751
00:31:06,990 --> 00:31:08,620
Brother, to be honest,

752
00:31:08,890 --> 00:31:10,190
I'll run out of money

753
00:31:10,660 --> 00:31:12,910
after completing them.

754
00:31:23,520 --> 00:31:24,120
How about this?

755
00:31:24,430 --> 00:31:27,760
I can take you to ask Mr. Wu for help.

756
00:31:28,350 --> 00:31:29,750
I've been with him for half of my life anyway.

757
00:31:29,960 --> 00:31:32,270
Maybe he can do us this favor.

758
00:31:32,710 --> 00:31:33,220
Are you going or not?

759
00:31:34,550 --> 00:31:36,030
Can he be willing to lend me money?

760
00:31:36,650 --> 00:31:37,370
If he is willing,

761
00:31:38,020 --> 00:31:38,820
then I can vouch for you.

762
00:31:41,830 --> 00:31:42,870
Come, Mr. Zhao.

763
00:31:43,570 --> 00:31:45,590
Overseas returnees like you

764
00:31:45,940 --> 00:31:47,020
love this.

765
00:31:47,510 --> 00:31:48,590
I specially prepared it for you.

766
00:31:48,920 --> 00:31:50,070
I really can't accept the taste.

767
00:31:51,150 --> 00:31:52,380
Mr. Wu asked me here

768
00:31:53,110 --> 00:31:54,230
not just for coffee, right?

769
00:31:54,610 --> 00:31:55,720
Just say it.

770
00:31:56,490 --> 00:31:57,330
Didn't you promise

771
00:31:57,650 --> 00:31:58,950
to buy the 50,000 tons of steel of mine?

772
00:31:59,970 --> 00:32:02,010
The current situation is neither good

773
00:32:03,230 --> 00:32:04,430
for Feng nor for Qiu.

774
00:32:04,760 --> 00:32:05,600
How about this?

775
00:32:05,910 --> 00:32:08,430
You can pay us part of the deposit first

776
00:32:08,830 --> 00:32:10,230
so that I can let them rest assured

777
00:32:10,610 --> 00:32:11,470
as their big brother.

778
00:32:13,510 --> 00:32:14,070
The deposit?

779
00:32:15,750 --> 00:32:17,190
Sure, no problem.

780
00:32:18,010 --> 00:32:19,340
Great. Thank you.

781
00:32:19,580 --> 00:32:20,190
Thank you, Mr. Zhao.

782
00:32:20,390 --> 00:32:21,980
Ten percent. Is that OK?

783
00:32:22,590 --> 00:32:23,470
Of course.

784
00:32:23,990 --> 00:32:24,710
Thanks for your generosity.

785
00:32:24,710 --> 00:32:25,630
Thank you.

786
00:32:25,880 --> 00:32:26,830
But there's one problem.

787
00:32:27,630 --> 00:32:28,190
As you know,

788
00:32:28,310 --> 00:32:29,870
the steel price is not stable.

789
00:32:30,830 --> 00:32:32,830
It can change from 1,000 to 900 in a day,

790
00:32:32,990 --> 00:32:33,950
and then reach 1200 in another day.

791
00:32:34,910 --> 00:32:37,390
What price should we pay

792
00:32:38,380 --> 00:32:39,420
for the ten percent of the deposit?

793
00:32:41,910 --> 00:32:42,380
Right.

794
00:32:43,820 --> 00:32:45,230
Mr. Zhao, how about this?

795
00:32:45,820 --> 00:32:46,760
Let's take the average.

796
00:32:48,190 --> 00:32:48,710
How about 1,000?

797
00:32:49,350 --> 00:32:51,420
50 million for 50,000 tons.

798
00:32:51,990 --> 00:32:53,940
Ten percent of 50 million is okay, right?

799
00:32:55,520 --> 00:32:56,570
Mr. Wu, how about this?

800
00:32:57,580 --> 00:32:58,500
After the steel is brought here

801
00:32:58,910 --> 00:32:59,820
and arrives at the port,

802
00:33:00,420 --> 00:33:02,230
we can trade

803
00:33:02,250 --> 00:33:03,370
according to the price in that day.

804
00:33:04,100 --> 00:33:04,980
I'll decide

805
00:33:05,830 --> 00:33:06,350
the price of the steel.

806
00:33:06,990 --> 00:33:07,590
What do you think?

807
00:33:16,740 --> 00:33:18,290
Mr. Zhao, I mean...

808
00:33:18,760 --> 00:33:20,760
Right, you have a point.

809
00:33:21,580 --> 00:33:23,770
But it can be hard for me

810
00:33:24,270 --> 00:33:25,590
to bring the 50,000 tons of steel here.

811
00:33:25,790 --> 00:33:27,110
I can't guarantee

812
00:33:27,310 --> 00:33:28,770
what the final price will be

813
00:33:29,010 --> 00:33:30,340
when the steel arrives at the port.

814
00:33:30,790 --> 00:33:32,980
You can't let me

815
00:33:33,230 --> 00:33:34,320
be like your laborer, right?

816
00:33:34,650 --> 00:33:35,090
How do you think?

817
00:33:36,140 --> 00:33:36,510
Come in.

818
00:33:36,930 --> 00:33:37,450
Hold on.

819
00:33:37,950 --> 00:33:38,390
Boss.

820
00:33:38,480 --> 00:33:38,930
Mr. Wu.

821
00:33:39,170 --> 00:33:40,130
Why are you here?

822
00:33:41,270 --> 00:33:41,980
Mr. Zhao is here.

823
00:33:42,470 --> 00:33:42,910
Mr. Zhao.

824
00:33:44,780 --> 00:33:45,350
What's up?

825
00:33:45,510 --> 00:33:45,870
Mr. Wu,

826
00:33:46,150 --> 00:33:46,990
since you have a guest,

827
00:33:47,530 --> 00:33:48,730
let's talk about this later.

828
00:33:48,830 --> 00:33:49,430
I’m leaving.

829
00:33:49,430 --> 00:33:50,470
No, wait.

830
00:33:50,560 --> 00:33:51,850
Well...

831
00:33:52,210 --> 00:33:53,310
You can talk first.

832
00:33:53,310 --> 00:33:54,510
We can wait next door.

833
00:33:54,620 --> 00:33:55,350
-Okay. -Don't...

834
00:33:55,380 --> 00:33:57,230
You go first. We're not in a hurry.

835
00:33:57,230 --> 00:33:58,590
-We can talk later. -Wait, Mr. Zhao, this...

836
00:33:58,610 --> 00:33:59,340
This is a big deal.

837
00:33:59,510 --> 00:34:00,990
They have nothing important.

838
00:34:01,010 --> 00:34:02,000
Just say it and leave.

839
00:34:03,190 --> 00:34:05,270
Xu's going to purchase scrap steel with us, right?

840
00:34:05,630 --> 00:34:07,590
She came to borrow money from me. But how can I have the money?

841
00:34:07,950 --> 00:34:10,489
I just want to borrow some money from you.

842
00:34:10,989 --> 00:34:13,190
Xu, don't bother.

843
00:34:13,520 --> 00:34:14,440
I'll give you 5,000 tons.

844
00:34:14,530 --> 00:34:15,600
And you don't need to go.

845
00:34:15,909 --> 00:34:17,710
Isn't it good for you to earn money without paying anything?

846
00:34:17,730 --> 00:34:19,929
Mr. Wu, we've reached an agreement last time.

847
00:34:20,020 --> 00:34:22,000
You promised to give me 15,000 tons.

848
00:34:22,030 --> 00:34:23,270
Why is it changed to 5,000 tons?

849
00:34:23,270 --> 00:34:24,429
When did I promise you?

850
00:34:24,489 --> 00:34:25,380
Please reconsider it.

851
00:34:26,030 --> 00:34:27,949
Why are you talking about this now?

852
00:34:28,159 --> 00:34:29,199
You're just a little girl.

853
00:34:29,510 --> 00:34:31,239
Don't always think about making money now.

854
00:34:31,949 --> 00:34:33,070
Your priority now

855
00:34:33,139 --> 00:34:34,730
is to find a good man and get married.

856
00:34:34,880 --> 00:34:36,280
Good men have all gotten married.

857
00:34:36,530 --> 00:34:36,840
Well...

858
00:34:37,190 --> 00:34:38,630
I'm still young. If I don't want to make money,

859
00:34:38,630 --> 00:34:39,230
then what should I think about?

860
00:34:39,620 --> 00:34:40,030
Mr. Wu,

861
00:34:40,870 --> 00:34:41,710
I have a storage yard.

862
00:34:41,949 --> 00:34:43,310
You can just put your scrap steel

863
00:34:43,340 --> 00:34:44,219
in my storage yard

864
00:34:44,520 --> 00:34:45,710
so that you can save a lot of money.

865
00:34:45,909 --> 00:34:46,800
Absolutely tall talk.

866
00:34:47,110 --> 00:34:48,389
Where is your storage yard?

867
00:34:48,389 --> 00:34:49,510
I can take you to see it.

868
00:34:49,989 --> 00:34:50,980
Fine.

869
00:34:51,130 --> 00:34:51,730
I believe you.

870
00:34:51,770 --> 00:34:53,739
I'll think about it if you really have a storage yard.

871
00:34:53,949 --> 00:34:54,270
Okay?

872
00:34:54,300 --> 00:34:55,190
I have important things to talk.

873
00:34:55,580 --> 00:34:56,420
Just leave. Hurry.

874
00:34:58,710 --> 00:35:00,670
Feng, say something for me.

875
00:35:00,710 --> 00:35:02,420
Didn't you promise to vouch for me?

876
00:35:02,710 --> 00:35:05,150
Don't you see boss is busy?

877
00:35:05,430 --> 00:35:07,270
Just take the amount he gives you.

878
00:35:07,960 --> 00:35:09,090
How can you be like this?

879
00:35:09,350 --> 00:35:10,590
I won't cover for you next time.

880
00:35:11,190 --> 00:35:12,070
What's wrong with you two?

881
00:35:12,550 --> 00:35:13,470
Covering for what?

882
00:35:14,040 --> 00:35:15,320
Feng, I'm not blaming you.

883
00:35:15,500 --> 00:35:16,750
Can you be serious?

884
00:35:17,310 --> 00:35:18,790
Your family is a mess.

885
00:35:18,790 --> 00:35:20,990
Your factory would've gone bankrupt without your wife.

886
00:35:21,790 --> 00:35:22,990
Mr. Wu, I'm leaving.

887
00:35:23,550 --> 00:35:24,310
You guys continue.

888
00:35:24,310 --> 00:35:24,750
Mr. Zhao.

889
00:35:25,110 --> 00:35:25,720
-Mr. Zhao. -I mean...

890
00:35:25,880 --> 00:35:26,350
Mr. Zhao.

891
00:35:26,590 --> 00:35:27,030
Mr. Wu.

892
00:35:27,430 --> 00:35:28,070
You two...

893
00:35:28,230 --> 00:35:29,470
My important matter gets screwed up because of you!

894
00:35:29,500 --> 00:35:30,500
Mr. Wu, you...

895
00:35:31,340 --> 00:35:32,240
What's wrong with you?

896
00:35:32,270 --> 00:35:33,310
How can you be like this?

897
00:35:33,310 --> 00:35:34,510
Wait, I was helping you with your matters...

898
00:35:34,510 --> 00:35:35,230
W-W-Why would you mention my...

899
00:35:35,230 --> 00:35:36,430
Tell me, what should I do with the money?

900
00:35:36,430 --> 00:35:37,310
W-W-Why would you mention my affair...

901
00:35:37,310 --> 00:35:38,990
You stepped on me...

902
00:35:40,150 --> 00:35:41,230
Damn Qiu.

903
00:35:41,760 --> 00:35:43,180
So ruthless!

904
00:35:43,870 --> 00:35:44,230
Paper.

905
00:35:48,090 --> 00:35:48,610
How about

906
00:35:49,690 --> 00:35:50,690
going to the hospital?

907
00:35:51,430 --> 00:35:51,910
It's okay.

908
00:35:58,330 --> 00:35:59,490
Isn't that Qiu Bizheng's car?

909
00:36:06,310 --> 00:36:06,830
Go see it.

910
00:36:07,300 --> 00:36:07,780
Be polite.

911
00:36:09,700 --> 00:36:10,260
Go.

912
00:36:15,840 --> 00:36:16,330
Where is Mr. Guo?

913
00:36:17,270 --> 00:36:18,070
He's resting in his room.

914
00:36:18,270 --> 00:36:19,030
He fell down

915
00:36:19,510 --> 00:36:20,420
and broke his nose.

916
00:36:33,550 --> 00:36:33,910
Brother.

917
00:36:34,500 --> 00:36:35,070
What is this?

918
00:36:35,780 --> 00:36:36,750
The dishes Mr. Qiu brought.

919
00:36:37,110 --> 00:36:38,230
Is this a place for putting dishes?

920
00:36:38,500 --> 00:36:38,940
Take them down.

921
00:36:42,300 --> 00:36:43,830
Don't think that I appreciate it

922
00:36:44,100 --> 00:36:45,670
that you hide the fact

923
00:36:46,190 --> 00:36:47,310
that I beat you from your families.

924
00:36:48,230 --> 00:36:49,110
Why are you standing here?

925
00:36:50,030 --> 00:36:50,550
Get out.

926
00:36:54,070 --> 00:36:55,360
You traitor!

927
00:36:55,590 --> 00:36:56,890
You ungrateful bastard!

928
00:36:57,550 --> 00:36:58,870
You haven't made it clear yet.

929
00:36:59,240 --> 00:37:00,110
You just leave

930
00:37:00,400 --> 00:37:01,390
and quit?

931
00:37:01,540 --> 00:37:02,650
What do you want?

932
00:37:05,960 --> 00:37:07,020
What do you want to eat?

933
00:37:21,040 --> 00:37:23,310
[Binhai City, Jiangdong Province]

934
00:37:21,040 --> 00:37:23,310
[Banxia Steel Co., LTD.]

935
00:37:35,250 --> 00:37:35,910
Hello.

936
00:37:36,820 --> 00:37:37,300
Who are you looking for?

937
00:37:38,540 --> 00:37:39,140
This is my dad.

938
00:37:41,940 --> 00:37:42,950
Is he your employee?

939
00:37:45,750 --> 00:37:46,480
You're so busy.

940
00:37:49,430 --> 00:37:52,800
Even a junk store owner can own a company.

941
00:38:08,190 --> 00:38:08,590
What do you mean?

942
00:38:08,830 --> 00:38:09,270
Write...

943
00:38:09,900 --> 00:38:10,430
Write what?

944
00:38:10,830 --> 00:38:11,660
IOU.

945
00:38:16,500 --> 00:38:17,250
Write as I say.

946
00:38:18,630 --> 00:38:19,400
IOU.

947
00:38:19,720 --> 00:38:21,640
I hereby acknowledge myself to be indebted to Xu Youren

948
00:38:21,830 --> 00:38:24,750
in the sum of RMB300,000.

949
00:38:25,140 --> 00:38:26,290
The debt must be paid back within half a year

950
00:38:26,900 --> 00:38:28,650
with the interest of RMB30,000,

951
00:38:28,870 --> 00:38:30,680
coming to a grand total of RMB330,000.

952
00:38:31,040 --> 00:38:33,560
If I can't pay it back before the due date,

953
00:38:34,700 --> 00:38:35,710
I shall be at the creditor's disposal.

954
00:38:36,510 --> 00:38:38,550
Name, Xu Banxia.

955
00:38:39,070 --> 00:38:40,470
Yes, date, date.

956
00:38:43,990 --> 00:38:44,470
And this...

957
00:38:47,150 --> 00:38:48,560
Are you really my father?

958
00:38:48,720 --> 00:38:49,990
Yes, of course.

959
00:38:51,970 --> 00:38:53,500
This is the due procedure.

960
00:38:54,150 --> 00:38:54,820
Get some water.

961
00:38:57,670 --> 00:38:58,070
Money.

962
00:38:59,770 --> 00:39:00,690
Do you have money here?

963
00:39:01,240 --> 00:39:01,650
The Real Estate Ownership Certificate.

964
00:39:02,990 --> 00:39:03,870
The Real Estate Ownership Certificate?

965
00:39:04,150 --> 00:39:04,670
Yes.

966
00:39:06,250 --> 00:39:07,850
Why are you looking at me like this?

967
00:39:08,270 --> 00:39:09,980
Qian's mother gave me the money.

968
00:39:10,010 --> 00:39:12,020
I have to get the certificate back as she requires it,

969
00:39:12,220 --> 00:39:12,620
right?

970
00:39:12,640 --> 00:39:14,060
Otherwise, I can't explain where the money is.

971
00:39:14,360 --> 00:39:15,760
You're making things difficult for me!

972
00:39:15,850 --> 00:39:17,330
How would I?

973
00:39:17,350 --> 00:39:19,720
We've been living in the house...

974
00:39:19,840 --> 00:39:20,590
But you came to make a scene...

975
00:39:20,830 --> 00:39:21,390
Look, who's making things difficult?

976
00:39:21,390 --> 00:39:23,790
Yes, you've been living happily there.

977
00:39:23,990 --> 00:39:25,590
But I didn't really do anything to you either.

978
00:39:25,610 --> 00:39:26,490
We've indeed been in the house,

979
00:39:26,760 --> 00:39:27,970
but your messing around

980
00:39:28,000 --> 00:39:29,550
can affect my family's happiness.

981
00:39:29,580 --> 00:39:30,900
Do you know what this is called?

982
00:39:31,800 --> 00:39:32,480
Selfish.

983
00:39:32,800 --> 00:39:34,150
You only think about yourself.

984
00:39:34,320 --> 00:39:36,000
You never thought about others' feelings.

985
00:39:36,150 --> 00:39:37,100
Have you ever thought for me?

986
00:39:37,130 --> 00:39:38,140
Of course I have.

987
00:39:38,390 --> 00:39:39,260
You're a boss

988
00:39:39,280 --> 00:39:40,120
and have an office.

989
00:39:40,420 --> 00:39:42,220
And our family needs to count on you.

990
00:39:42,240 --> 00:39:43,320
This is your ability.

991
00:39:43,350 --> 00:39:45,000
So I must do anything for you just because I'm capable?

992
00:39:45,020 --> 00:39:45,380
Is this what you think?

993
00:39:45,470 --> 00:39:46,440
Buy whatever you want.

994
00:39:46,470 --> 00:39:47,610
I've even been giving you money each month.

995
00:39:47,640 --> 00:39:48,720
I owe you?

996
00:39:48,750 --> 00:39:50,270
